text: David Prentice (29 July 1908–1984) was a Scottish professional footballer who played in the Football League for Mansfield Town and Walsall. ==References== Category:1908 births Category:1984 deaths Category:Scottish footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:English Football League players Category:Celtic F.C. players Category:Stranraer F.C. players Category:Ayr United F.C. players Category:Nithsdale Wanderers F.C. players Category:Plymouth Argyle F.C. players Category:Walsall F.C. players Category:AFC Bournemouth players Category:Raith Rovers F.C. players Category:Mansfield Town F.C. players Category:Bath City F.C. players Category:Trowbridge Town F.C. players
